'''塞思·伍迪贝瑞·麦克法兰'''（{{lang-en|Seth Woodbury MacFarlane}}，{{bd|1973年|10月26日}}）是一位两度获得[[艾美奖|艾美奖]]的美国喜剧演员、[[动画师|动画师]]、[[编剧|编剧]]、[[电视制片人|电视制片人]]、[[演员|演员]]、[[配音演员|配音演员]]以及作词家。塞思·麦克法兰最为有名的作品是他为[[福克斯广播公司|福克斯广播公司]]创作的动画片《[[蓋酷家庭|蓋酷家庭]]》及《[[特工老爹|特工老爹]]》。他在2012年导演兼编剧兼配音的电影《[[泰迪熊_(电影)|熊麻吉]]》曾是全球票房收入最高的限制级喜剧电影。他也曾是系列电视片《赢家》的制作人。

麦克法兰为他自己的卡通片的许多角色配音，比如《蓋酷家庭》中的[[Peter_Griffin|Peter Griffin]]、[[Stewie_Griffin|Stewie Griffin]]、[[Brian_Griffin|Brian Griffin]]、[[Glen_Quagmire|Glen Quagmire]] 以及《特工老爹》中的 [[Stan_Smith|Stan Smith]] 与 [[Roger_(American_Dad!)|Roger the Alien]]。作为一个演员，他在各种节目中客串演出，包括有《[[Gilmore_Girls|Gilmore Girls]]》与《[[家庭战争|家庭战争]]》。麦克法兰也是一位科幻迷，他在《星际旅行：企业号》中客串演出过，并且曾经在自己的动画片中幽默地模仿过《[[星球大战|星球大战]]》与《[[星际旅行|星际旅行]]》。作为一个很受欢迎的演讲者，他有时会在美国各个高校进行演讲。他本人支持美国[[民主黨_(美國)|民主党]]并且在[[2007-08年美国编剧协会大罢工|2007-08年美国编剧协会大罢工]]中公开支持作家协会。

== 早期生活 ==
麦克法兰于1973年10月26日出生于美国[[康涅狄格州|康涅狄格州]]的肯特镇。<ref>[http://movies.ign.com/articles/429/429628p1.html "An Interview with Seth MacFarlane: The creator of Family Guy discusses his career."] {{Wayback|url=http://movies.ign.com/articles/429/429628p1.html |date=20120206214630 }} p. 1. IGN. Published 2003-07-21. Retrieved 2007-12-20.</ref> 他的父母Ann Perry Sager 与 Ronald Milton MacFarlane来自于[[马萨诸塞州|马萨诸塞州]]的Newburyport。麦克法兰在孩童时代时对插图画十分感兴趣。在一次《[[今日美国|今日美国]]》的采访中，他说到自己从那时就开始学着画[[Fred_Flintstone|Fred Flintstone]]与[[Woody_Woodpecker|Woody Woodpecker]]。<ref name="usatoday">{{cite news | first=Gary | last=Levin | coauthors= | title='Dad' joins 'Guy' for yuks | date=2005-02-02 | publisher=Gannett Co. Inc. | url=http://www.usatoday.com/life/television/news/2005-02-02-macfarlane_x.htm | work=USA Today | pages= | accessdate=2007-12-21 | language= | archive-date=2011-06-29 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110629120246/http://www.usatoday.com/life/television/news/2005-02-02-macfarlane_x.htm }}</ref> 1991年，他从康涅狄格州的肯特学院高中毕业。该校的校长Rev. Richardson W. Schell曾公开批评麦克法兰的幽默品位低下，并要求福克斯停止播映《蓋酷家庭》。<ref name="Weinraub">{{cite news | first=Bernard | last=Weinraub | coauthors= | title=The Young Guy Of ''Family Guy''; A 30-Year-Old's Cartoon Hit Makes An Unexpected Comeback | date=2005-04-07 | publisher=The New York Times Company | url=http://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?res=9D02E4D6173BF934A35754C0A9629C8B63&sec=&spon=&pagewanted=2 | work=The New York Times | pages= | accessdate=2007-12-22 | language= | archive-date=2008-01-10 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080110105932/http://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?res=9D02E4D6173BF934A35754C0A9629C8B63&sec=&spon=&pagewanted=2 }}</ref> 麦克法兰的父母都在这所学校教书，他们双双辞职表示抗议。<ref name="Weinraub"/><ref>Carter, Bill. [http://www.seattlepi.com/tv/guy01.shtml Advertisers shunning ''Family Guy'']. ''[[New_York_Times|New York Times]]''. Published 1999-07-01. Retrieved 2007-12-20.</ref><ref>via [[Associated_Press|Associated Press]]. [http://nl.newsbank.com/nl-search/we/Archives?p_product=ST&s_site=dfw&p_multi=ST&p_theme=realcities&p_action=search&p_maxdocs=200&p_topdoc=1&p_text_direct-0=0EAF920E64F34493&p_field_direct-0=document_id&p_perpage=10&p_sort=YMD_date:D&s_trackval=GooglePM "One-man campaign out for `Family Guy'"] {{Wayback|url=http://nl.newsbank.com/nl-search/we/Archives?p_product=ST&s_site=dfw&p_multi=ST&p_theme=realcities&p_action=search&p_maxdocs=200&p_topdoc=1&p_text_direct-0=0EAF920E64F34493&p_field_direct-0=document_id&p_perpage=10&p_sort=YMD_date:D&s_trackval=GooglePM |date=20210301201220 }}, ''[[Fort_Worth_Star-Telegram|Fort Worth Star-Telegram]]'', 1999-07-02. Accessed 2008-02-13. "Seth MacFarlane has been out of prep school for eight years, but the headmaster is still on his case. The top administrator of the Kent School is leading a one-man campaign to get advertisers to drop The Family Guy, an animated TV comedy created by MacFarlane, a 1991 Kent alumnus."</ref>

麦克法兰是在[[罗德岛设计学院|罗德岛设计学院]]（RISD）学习的动画设计。当他还是一名学生的时候，他曾想以后为[[华特迪士尼公司|华特迪士尼公司]]工作。后来当从RISD毕业时，他改变了想法。他回忆道“与许多动画家一样，我曾经认为迪士尼就是上帝。如今，迪士尼在我心目中变成了撒旦。”<ref name="yahoo">[http://tv.yahoo.com/seth-macfarlane/contributor/663655/bio;_ylt=Aon954w635FJbS9IA6nuh_2.o9EF "Seth MacFarlane - Biography"] {{Wayback|url=http://tv.yahoo.com/seth-macfarlane/contributor/663655/bio;_ylt=Aon954w635FJbS9IA6nuh_2.o9EF |date=20110615083612 }}. [[Yahoo|Yahoo]]. Retrieved 2007-12-20.</ref> 在大学期间，他创作了名为《[[Larry_shorts|The Life of Larry]]》的动画电影作为论文。<ref name="E">[https://web.archive.org/web/20071016201112/http://www.eonline.com/celebrities/profile/?uuid=a315fdae-d12b-4aef-9aaf-c3dac1bcf838 "Seth MacFarlane - Profile"]. ''[[E!|E!]] Online''. Retrieved 2007-12-20.</ref> 他在RISD的教授把麦克法兰的卡通片提交给了[[Hanna-Barbera|Hanna-Barbera]]，后者后来雇请了麦克法兰。<ref name="yahoo"/> 在十多年后的2007年6月2日，麦克法兰在母校的毕业典礼上获得荣誉博士头衔。<ref>[http://www.projo.com/news/content/RISDGRAD03_06-03-07_MG5SHIT.31ebed6.html "The art of graduating goes to a higher plane at RISD ceremony"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.projo.com/news/content/RISDGRAD03_06-03-07_MG5SHIT.31ebed6.html |date=20080410220902 }} ''The Providence Journal''. Retrieved 2007-06-03.</ref>

== 动画及电视职业生涯 ==
在Hanna-Barbera的时候，麦克法兰的主要工作是一名动画师以及为[[Cartoon_Network|Cartoon Network]]的《[[卡通卡通|卡通卡通]]》系列进行剧作。<ref>[http://movies.ign.com/articles/429/429628p3.html "An Interview with Seth MacFarlane: The creator of Family Guy discusses his career."] {{Wayback|url=http://movies.ign.com/articles/429/429628p3.html |date=20120113091539 }} p. 3. IGN. Published 2003-07-21. Retrieved 2007-12-20.</ref> 他也曾经为《[[拼命郎約翰尼|拼命郎約翰尼]]》，《[[鸡与牛|鸡与牛]]》，和《[[德克斯特的实验室|德克斯特的实验室]]》工作过。麦克法兰也曾在[[尼克国际儿童频道|尼克国际儿童频道]]为[[Frederator_Studio|Frederator Studio]]的《[[Oh_Yeah!_Cartoons|Oh Yeah! Cartoons]]》创作过一部名为《Zoomates》的短片动画。<ref>[http://newtoons.frederator.com/post/4687 " Answers. Fred Seibert's Blog"] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080113063039/http://newtoons.frederator.com/post/4687 |date=2008-01-13 }}. Published 2007-11-01. Retrieved 2007-12-21.</ref>1996年，麦克法兰创作了一部名为《[[Larry_shorts|Larry and Steve]]》的短片作为《The Life of Larry》的续集，其描述了一位名叫Larry的中年角色与一只具有智力的名为Steve的狗的故事。这部短片作为[[Cartoon_Network|Cartoon Network]]的《[[What-A-Cartoon!|World Premiere Toons]]》节目进行播映。[[福克斯广播公司|福克斯广播公司]]的主管人员看到了这部动画，其后与麦克法兰签下了合同创作《蓋酷家庭》系列。<ref name="Bartlett">{{cite web|url = http://greatreporter.com/mambo/content/view/1383/11/|title = Seth MacFarlane – he’s the “Family Guy”|accessdate = 2007-12-31|last = Bartlett|first = James|date = 2007-03-12|work = greatreporter.com|publisher = Presswire Limited|quote = ... his company, Fuzzy Door Productions ...|archive-date = 2010-11-23|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20101123072607/http://greatreporter.com/mambo/content/view/1383/11/|dead-url = no}}</ref>  麦克法兰在24岁就成为电视界最年轻的[[执行制作人|执行制作人]]。<ref name="usatoday"/> 福克斯提议麦克法兰制作一部15分钟短片并资助他5万美元。麦克法兰说这部《蓋酷家庭》试播的创作与制作一共花了六个月。<ref name="tenquestionstwo">{{cite web |url=http://www.mania.com/39617.html |title=DVD Interview: 10 Questions with FAMILY GUY's Seth McFarlane - Part One |publisher=ManiaDVD |accessdate=2007-12-21 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080110124052/http://www.mania.com/39617.html |archivedate=2008-01-10 }}</ref> 在一次《[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]》的采访中，麦克法兰说：“在大约六个月中，我几乎没有睡眠，没有其它活动，只是疯狂地在我的厨房里画画与制作这部试播片。”<ref>{{cite news | first=Bernard | last=Weinraub | coauthors= | title=The Young Guy Of 'Family Guy'; A 30-Year-Old's Cartoon Hit Makes An Unexpected Comeback | date=2007-07-07 | publisher=The New York Times Company | url=http://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?res=9D02E4D6173BF934A35754C0A9629C8B63&sec=&spon=&pagewanted=2 | work=''The New York Times'' | pages=2 | accessdate=2008-01-06 | language= | archive-date=2008-01-10 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080110105932/http://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?res=9D02E4D6173BF934A35754C0A9629C8B63&sec=&spon=&pagewanted=2 }}</ref> 麦克法兰于2008年5月与福克斯签下了价值1亿美元的协议来继续为福克斯创作《蓋酷家庭》与《特工老爹》至2012年，这使他成为了世界上薪酬最高的电视剧作者。<ref>[http://www.buddytv.com/articles/family-guy/family-guy-creator-signs-lucra-19173.aspx ''Family Guy'' Creator Signs Lucrative Deal with FOX.] {{Wayback|url=http://www.buddytv.com/articles/family-guy/family-guy-creator-signs-lucra-19173.aspx |date=20160115154922 }} BuddyTV. 2008-05-07. Retrieved on 2008-05-14.</ref>

=== 《蓋酷家庭》 ===
{{main|蓋酷家庭}}
