麦克法兰参与过[[2007-08年美国编剧协会大罢工|2007-08年美国编剧协会大罢工]]。<ref>[http://wga.org/subpage_member.aspx?id=2529 "Pencils Down"] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071219203656/http://www.wga.org/subpage_member.aspx?id=2529 |date=2007-12-19 }}. Writers' Guild of America. Retrieved 2007-12-20.</ref> 罢工期间，福克斯没有经过麦克法兰同意继续制作《蓋酷家庭》与《特工老爹》。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.eonline.com/news/article/index.jsp?uuid=d7677427-c425-4264-b6a2-bd64c9159a07 |title=Fox's ''Family'' Sans Guy |accessdate=2007-12-22 |last=Grossberg |first=Josh |date=2007-11-14 |work=E! News |publisher=E! Online}}</ref>

=== 《特工老爹》 ===    	
