mes Company | url=http://www.nytimes.com/2005/02/04/arts/04tvwk.html?_r=1&fta=y&oref=slogin | work=The New York Times | pages= | accessdate=2007-12-22 | language= | archive-date=2013-05-09 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130509174838/http://www.nytimes.com/2005/02/04/arts/04tvwk.html?_r=1&fta=y&oref=slogin }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | first=Jay | last=Goyette | coauthors= | title=Family Guy's Seth MacFarlane's Speech Rescheduled | date=2005-02-04 | publisher=University of Vermont | url=http://www.uvm.edu/theview/article.php?id=1561 | work=The View | pages= | accessdate=2007-12-22 | language= | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080110051921/http://www.uvm.edu/theview/article.php?id=1561 | archivedate=2008-01-10 }}</ref> 塞思·麦克法兰为Stan与Roger配音。塞思的妹妹 [[:en:Rachael_MacFarlane|Rachel]] 是 Hayley 的配音員。

