=== 《The Cleveland Show》 ===
{{main|The Cleveland Show}}
麦克法兰正在制作《蓋酷家庭》的外传《The Cleveland Show》。这部外传将主要集中在《蓋酷家庭》中的角色[[Cleveland_Brown|Cleveland Brown]]及其一家。这个主意源于Cleveland的配音同时也是《蓋酷家庭》的作者[[Mike_Henry_(television_writer/producer)|Mike Henry]]的建议。福克斯已经预订了13集。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://tv.ign.com/articles/871/871629p1.html |title=Big New Deal for Family Guy's Seth MacFarlane |author=Eric Goldman |publisher=[[IGN|IGN]] |date=2008-05-05 |accessdate=2008-05-05 |archive-date=2012-05-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120516185527/http://tv.ign.com/articles/871/871629p1.html }}</ref>

