[[File:Seth_mcfarlane_speaks_at_wga_rally.jpg|right]]集会上讲话，[[Culver_City,_California|Culver City]]。]]
麦克法兰是一位《[[星球大战|星球大战]]》与《[[星际旅行|星际旅行]]》的狂热爱好者，同时也是一位[[科幻小说|科幻小说]]迷。<ref name="startrek">[http://www.startrek.com/startrek/view/news/article/8695.html "Production Report: Klingon Discrepancy Addressed in 'Affliction'"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.startrek.com/startrek/view/news/article/8695.html |date=20090309012957 }}. ''Star Trek'' Online. Published 2004-12-16. Retrieved 2007-12-20.</ref><ref name="adalian1">Adalian, Josef. [http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117965865.html?categoryid=14&cs=1 "''Family Guy'' meets ''Star Wars'': Toon kicking off season with approved spoof"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117965865.html?categoryid=14&cs=1 |date=20090226111833 }}. ''Variety''. Published 2007-05-25. Retrieved 2007-12-20.</ref> 在音乐方面， 他是一位娴熟的钢琴演奏者与[[男中音|男中音]]歌唱家。年輕時，他曾和[[弗兰克·西纳特拉|弗兰克·西纳特拉]]和[[芭芭拉·史翠珊|芭芭拉·史翠珊]]合作过， 也與他們師出同門（不同時期受教），所以不提倡用電子矯音，唱歌時也著重露出牙齒，令咬字清楚、精確。<ref name="Bartlett"/> 他也观看电视剧《[[黑道家族|黑道家族]]》与《[[马赫脱口秀|马赫脱口秀]]》。<ref name="personal">{{cite news|first=Thomas |last=McLean |coauthors= |title=Seth MacFarlane: ''Family Guy,'' ''American Dad!'' |date=2007-06-01 |publisher=Reed Business |url=http://www.variety.com/awardcentral_article/VR1117966166.html?nav=eproducer07 |work=Variety |pages= |accessdate=2008-01-05 |language= |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20121205083707/http://www.variety.com/awardcentral |archivedate=2012-12-05 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>

